{"tid":2269680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"14歲少年寓所外牆練習游繩墮下　清醒送院　父母涉疏忽照顧被捕 (20:32)","createTime":"2020-11-03T14:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T03:22:24.000Z","uid":285365,"like":154,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5e2acd9019cf6dec85636c769c3a98b9b55a5898","tid":2269680,"uid":285365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"下午2時許，一名14歲少年在鰂魚涌柏蕙苑康柏閣寓所外牆練習游繩之際，從高處墮下至2樓平台，清醒送院。警方到場，經調查後將其六旬父母拘捕，涉嫌疏忽照顧兒童。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該名少年早前在學校學游繩，今午在其13樓家中爬出外牆練習游繩，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">其父親則在2樓平台等候他</span></span>，詎料游繩途中跌至平台，其母當時亦在家中。警方正調查少年在哪一層墮下。現場所見，大廈外牆遺下一條繩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMjKuTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMjKuTJ.jpg&h=dc756b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟佢地成家係咪都係智障？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60bd08c0ac3e9c15780aa24a0900113eb7d005e5","tid":2269680,"uid":136416,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"cls<br />\n估唔到一直以黎ff既事真係有人做<br />\n仲要失手墜樓"},{"pid":"170c347a0414438c475de25584fcf272ac7e4d08","tid":2269680,"uid":285365,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"60bd08c0ac3e9c15780aa24a0900113eb7d005e5","tid":2269680,"uid":136416,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"cls<br />\n估唔到一直以黎ff既事真係有人做<br />\n仲要失手墜樓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"其實條𡃁仔係咪好似電視劇咁綁住窗框或者枱腳就跳落樓"},{"pid":"01a3ec6568963cbc699688db363b518e4589fdfb","tid":2269680,"uid":57929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"好撚癲"},{"pid":"531186c624c433d2fa68d855870d9fecc370b37f","tid":2269680,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:58:44.000Z","msg":".....<i